{"title":"海峡抒情短章（二首）","authors":["曾凡华"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海峡抒情短章（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾凡华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜金门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条卧蚕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匍匐于夜海的网络里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉入休眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唇边游移的丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缠住西坠的落月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颤颤噤噤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思乡的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羽化为一只扑朔的飞蛾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着被太阳吻化的雪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐着旷野的清风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿鲜鲜的春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把水灵灵的雁叫声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种进了北方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，吹响了暖洋洋的口哨吹响了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《生命圆舞曲》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方，不再是悲哀的了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每滴雨都是鼓满激情的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，这里将旺盛地生长着一首首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂扬的抒情诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推土机翻耕着淡绿的山色翻耕着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被冬冻僵了的遥梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羞涩的心象迎春花般"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵一朵地开放着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过固执的鹿砦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落脚在某一片记忆的丝叶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死死地、死死地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与之相吻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——每逢佳节，沿海军民都用氢气球把大陆土特产飘送过海峡……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把乳白的椭圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送上青空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托付给不定的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不定飘零于哪片荒野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不定失落在哪座死城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我坚信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论委堕于何处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总会溅起一点回声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕勾几缕相思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕牵一丝离情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会象稍纵即逝的肥皂泡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅留下些纷呈的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿这不计代价的给予"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能收回一颗归来的心……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}